column5: Are you folks up in canada having enough snow this year that lake of the woods will back to normal? I look at the cabiin camera and the snow looks like you dont have too much. what do you think? thanks
Hello anyone? I know the nights or long but you have to get up sometime. at least you must have seen Janet Jackson boob right? Or was it her left. Oh never mind

Don't know about the LOTW area, but I did see in the Sioux Lookout paper last week that they have had significantly more snow than usual in January. Let's hope that translates to all of of MW Ontario.
